00:00.845 --> 00:04.437
ï»¿Look for the bare necessities.

00:04.622 --> 00:07.001
The simple bare necessities.

00:07.099 --> 00:10.219
Forget about your worries and your strife.

00:11.700 --> 00:17.465
I mean the bare necessities, old Mother Nature's recipes,...

00:17.552 --> 00:21.160
...that bring the bare necessities of life.

00:22.155 --> 00:31.515
