00:38.343 --> 00:40.971
When you look under the rocks and plants...

00:41.056 --> 00:47.523
...and take a glance at the fancy ants, then maybe try a few.

00:48.222 --> 00:51.950
The bare necessities of life will come to you.

00:53.005 --> 00:54.790
They'll come to you!

